  "description": "The open sky seen from 200m below the surface: diffuse, dark blue, impossibly far away. OpenSky's shimmer reverb becomes the water column itself. Supersaw spread is minimal — only one voice, thick with water pressure. The RISE macro becomes a slow ascent toward the surface.",
